channel.title: ASF Jira
channel.description: This file is an XML representation of an issue

item.title: [HIVE-21048] Remove needless org.mortbay.jetty from hadoop exclusions
item.description:
During HIVE-20638 i found that org.mortbay.jetty exclusions from e.g. hadoop don't take effect, as the actual groupId of jetty is org.eclipse.jetty for most of the current projects, please find attachment (example for hive commons project).

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jetty_(web_server)#History
item.summary: Remove needless org.mortbay.jetty from hadoop exclusions

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
